# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Contact form — Web3Forms
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Setup (about 2 minutes, no account needed):
#   1. Visit https://web3forms.com and enter  muhammednazila@gmail.com
#   2. Web3Forms emails you an Access Key (a UUID). Copy it.
#   3. Duplicate this file as ".env" (git-ignored) and paste the key below.
#   4. Restart the dev server, and set the same var in your host (Vercel/Netlify).
#
# This key is SAFE to ship in the client bundle — submissions are delivered only
# to the email the key is bound to. For extra hardening, enable a domain
# allow-list (and optionally hCaptcha) from your Web3Forms dashboard.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key-here
